data.description: Stunning waterfront home in desired Landstown Meadows. First floor primary with attached full bath. Open and airy floor plan. Cathedral ceilings and wood burning fireplace. Modern kitchen has high-end stainless steel appliances, island, and custom backsplash. Two spacious bedrooms on second floor with attached full bath. Additional loft space overlooking first level. Jetted tub and outdoor shower are "as is". Partially converted garage. Tranquil views of the water from the living room. Convenient to several shops and restaurants.
